java.lang.Object

se.citerus.dddsample.domain.model.cargo.RouteSpecification
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Specification<Itinerary>, ValueObject<RouteSpecification>
@Embeddable public class RouteSpecification extends AbstractSpecification<Itinerary> implements ValueObject<RouteSpecification>
Route specification. Describes where a cargo origin and destination is, and the arrival deadline.
